-----Project Overview------

This project analyzes sales performance using Python. It focuses on revenue, profitability, customer behavior, regional growth, and sales representative performance.
Strong Business Insights

•	Total Revenue: ₹5,019,265.23
•	Total Profit: ₹6,487,847.07
•	Top Region: North
•	Top Product Category: Clothing
•	Best Sales Representative: David
•	Most Used Payment Method: Credit Card

------Business Recommendations---------

1.	Increase marketing in top-performing regions.
2.	Focus on high-profit product categories.
3.	Reduce unnecessary discounts to improve profit margins.
4.	Use loyalty programs for returning customers.
5.	Train low-performing sales reps using top performers' strategy.
